data.description: Welcome to your home on Ravenridge! Enjoy this lovely single story home and fully-fenced back yard. This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home is warm and inviting and just minutes away from Long Lake, shopping, highway, and the ferry. Whether someone works remotely or has to go into the office, this home is situated in a place that allows for multiple commuting options. Featuring vinyl and laminate hardwood floors, bay windows, wood fireplace, dedicated dining space, large and bright open kitchen with stainless appliances, entertainment-ready deck, primary bedroom with en suite, and den/office. Enjoy the privacy but also the closeness to town or even an adventure into the city. Help make this house a home and enjoy your life's next chapter.
